#: ../../compositing/blending_modes.rst:18
msgid ""
"Blending modes (or **blend modes** or **mixing modes**) are also called "
"**Composition Type** in Kdenlive. They determine how two images are blended "
"together. The default blending mode is simply to cover whatever is in the "
"lower track by whatever is in the upper track, while taking any :ref:`alpha "
"channel <compositing-alpha_channels>` information into account."
msgstr ""
"Mengmodes (or **mix-modes**) worden ook in Kdenlive **Compositie Type** "
"genoemd. Ze bepalen hoe twee afbeeldingen samen worden gemengd. De standaard "
"mengmode is gewoon bedekken wat in de onderliggende track is door wat in de "
"bovenliggende track aanwezig is, terwijl er met de informatie in het :ref:"
"`alfakanaal <compositing-alpha_channels>` rekening wordt gehouden."

#: ../../compositing/blending_modes.rst:20
msgid ""
"In this section, we are using the :guilabel:`Composition Type` **Cairo "
"Blend** to explain the different blend modes."
msgstr ""
"In deze sectie gebruiken we het :guilabel:`Compositietype` **Cairoblend** "
"bij de uitleg over de verschillende mengmodes."

#: ../../compositing/blending_modes.rst:22
msgid ""
"Compositing/blending needs at least two tracks: The top track or \"layer\", "
"also called the *blend layer* or *active layer*; and the \"bottom\" track or "
"layer, also called the *base layer*. In a blending composition, the *blend "
"layer* is always the track where the composition originates, whereas the "
"*base layer* can be specified with the :guilabel:`Composition track`. By "
"default it is set to :guilabel:`Automatic` which uses the track immediately "
"below."
msgstr ""
"Een compositie/menging heeft tenminste twee tracks nodig: De bovenliggende "
"track of \"laag\", die ook *menglaag* of *actieve laag* wordt genoemd; en de "
"\"onderliggende\" track of laag, ook wel de *basis laag* wordt genoemd. Bij "
"een meng-compositie is de *menglaag* altijd de track waar de compositie "
"origineel vandaan komt, waarbij de *basis laag* geselecteerd kan worden met :"
"guilabel:`Compositie track`. Standaard is deze ingesteld op :guilabel:"
"`Automatisch` die de track onmiddellijk eronder gebruikt."

